WEBVTT

00:00:55.300 --> 00:01:02.329
Open Your Heart, 4th Seminar Session, Lonavala (India), 25.01.1982

00:01:02.530 --> 00:01:06.491
It is such a pleasure to meet so many Sahaja Yogis

00:01:06.692 --> 00:01:12.025
from all over the world, and to be able to talk to them.

00:01:12.226 --> 00:01:16.644
They understand Me the best, in this whole world.

00:01:16.845 --> 00:01:19.968
It’s impossible to have a rapport

00:01:20.169 --> 00:01:24.556
with a person who is not a Sahaja Yogi.

00:01:24.757 --> 00:01:30.274
Even if you give them realization, if they have not become Sahaja Yogis,

00:01:30.474 --> 00:01:34.073
then it is very difficult to make them understand

00:01:34.273 --> 00:01:38.974
the subtleties of their own being also.

00:01:39.174 --> 00:01:46.743
Today, as we are all Sahaja Yogis here,

00:01:46.943 --> 00:01:53.422
I would like to tell you about the growth

00:01:53.623 --> 00:01:59.644
of the being on the subtler plane.

00:02:09.062 --> 00:02:16.773
All the time, as we have been doing anything,

00:02:16.974 --> 00:02:23.043
we have been thinking what is to be done?

00:02:23.243 --> 00:02:26.750
"What is to be done to be realized?" was the first question

00:02:26.951 --> 00:02:29.781
people asked Me, when they were not realized.

00:02:29.982 --> 00:02:33.502
"What should we do Mother to get realized?"

00:02:33.703 --> 00:02:35.796
Then I had to tell them, "Nothing, just spread

00:02:35.997 --> 00:02:39.594
your hands towards Me, and it will work out."

00:02:39.794 --> 00:02:44.456
It’s true, it works out that way. Now after realization,

00:02:44.657 --> 00:02:48.093
you have to do something, as they say.

00:02:48.293 --> 00:02:50.732
But still what have you to do? Again, the question comes in,

00:02:50.933 --> 00:02:54.893
"What should we do for this to remove this chakra, that chakra;

00:02:55.094 --> 00:02:58.635
what is the technique, what is the thing?"

00:02:58.836 --> 00:03:01.510
The trouble with Sahaja Yogis as they are today,

00:03:01.711 --> 00:03:06.712
they are all technocrats already.

00:03:06.913 --> 00:03:12.171
They have done so much of technical things, that it is better that they should forget about technique

00:03:12.372 --> 00:03:15.679
and worry more about spontaneity.

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:23.263
The technique is so much, that the technique has killed the spontaneity,

00:03:23.464 --> 00:03:29.654
and a balance has to be struck between technique and the spontaneity.

00:03:29.855 --> 00:03:36.054
First you get your realization by spontaneity, sahaja.

00:03:36.254 --> 00:03:42.101
Then you have to have – naturally, by temperament

00:03:42.302 --> 00:03:45.986
you are technocrats – want to have a technique,

00:03:46.187 --> 00:03:51.827
the tantra, the mechanism, how to work out the mechanism.

00:03:52.028 --> 00:03:56.405
Thank God, we are not so bad now, otherwise, normally,

00:03:56.606 --> 00:03:59.767
I have seen, I was giving lectures and people were giving

00:03:59.968 --> 00:04:04.220
bandhans to them and raising their Kundalini, all mad people around,

00:04:04.421 --> 00:04:08.162
and others who were newcomers would be frightened at such Sahaja Yogis

00:04:08.363 --> 00:04:13.882
that "What is the matter with these people? They are so abnormal."

00:04:15.544 --> 00:04:18.654
And if you tell them that you should not do it, you should just listen

00:04:18.855 --> 00:04:22.505
to the lecture, they would say, "No, no, Mother,

00:04:22.706 --> 00:04:29.048
we were catching, so we were trying to put ourselves right."

00:04:32.044 --> 00:04:39.287
Now one has to realize that you have to become subtler.

00:04:40.318 --> 00:04:43.974
Then again the question, "How to become?"

00:04:44.174 --> 00:04:48.568
How to become subtler is the problem.

00:04:48.769 --> 00:04:52.587
For example, today, there was a question of having a puja

00:04:52.788 --> 00:04:58.050
in the morning time, today. They said that there is a Suryagrahana,

00:04:58.251 --> 00:05:04.054
means the eclipse of the sun and if today is such a great date,

00:05:04.254 --> 00:05:10.936
that if you do the worship or the puja,

00:05:11.137 --> 00:05:15.858
you get blessings of thousands of such pujas

00:05:16.059 --> 00:05:20.074
on an eclipse day of the sun.

00:05:20.274 --> 00:05:28.666
Now, if you look at it, it looks very fine, good, yes it’s true,

00:05:28.867 --> 00:05:33.369
it is written in the astrological survey and all that,

00:05:33.570 --> 00:05:36.354
is a very great thing, and we start following it.

00:05:36.555 --> 00:05:43.694
You being Sahaja Yogis, you must attack it from a subtler point.

00:05:43.894 --> 00:05:48.178
That is how your wisdom will also become subtler;

00:05:48.378 --> 00:05:51.799
your attitude also will become subtler.

00:05:51.999 --> 00:05:54.564
To attack such a question from subtle point of view,

00:05:54.765 --> 00:06:00.017
we have to first of all know that we are Sahaja Yogis.

00:06:00.218 --> 00:06:03.356
No technique is needed, just see your vibrations on this question,

00:06:03.557 --> 00:06:09.378
to begin with, it’s very simple. Subtler things are the simpler things;

00:06:09.578 --> 00:06:12.029
gross things are complicated.

00:06:12.230 --> 00:06:16.615
It is very simple, very simple equation.

00:06:16.816 --> 00:06:19.942
Simple thing is to feel the vibrations on this point,

00:06:20.143 --> 00:06:25.700
whether today’s puja, is it really worth something or not?

00:06:25.901 --> 00:06:32.721
You’ll be amazed that your right side will become hot on this point.

00:06:32.922 --> 00:06:38.923
So, this intellect, which is now being enlightened,

00:06:39.124 --> 00:06:45.476
prabuddha you have become, you must use it in a subtler way.

00:06:45.677 --> 00:06:54.082
Why, that for Sahaja Yogis, it is not necessary to do the puja today?

00:06:56.230 --> 00:06:58.240
You have already become thoughtless,

00:06:58.441 --> 00:07:02.428
so I will not ask you to answer the question.

00:07:02.629 --> 00:07:11.738
The reason is, as you are all technocrats, you are right-sided.

00:07:12.862 --> 00:07:18.134
This was all right thousands of years back, when the Vedas started,

00:07:18.335 --> 00:07:21.910
and the Vedas have given us the science.

00:07:22.111 --> 00:07:27.714
All the excitement about Vedas was all right at that time

00:07:27.915 --> 00:07:32.126
when they worshipped the Surya or the right-sided things.

00:07:32.327 --> 00:07:36.025
In Greece, these things reached such a height

00:07:36.226 --> 00:07:39.011
that all the Gods had to fall just like human beings

00:07:39.212 --> 00:07:41.535
and become just like human beings.

00:07:41.736 --> 00:07:45.548
For them now, everybody has weaknesses; every God has a weakness.

00:07:45.749 --> 00:07:48.400
This weakness one has, that weakness another has,

00:07:48.601 --> 00:07:52.139
they don’t understand Gods anymore in Greece.

00:07:52.340 --> 00:07:54.829
They just think that they are some sort of entities

00:07:55.030 --> 00:07:59.274
with all the weaknesses of human beings burdened on them.

00:07:59.475 --> 00:08:05.648
So, this right side movement has been bit too much since the time of Vedas.

00:08:05.848 --> 00:08:10.851
Worshipping of Surya has been too much; you have worshipped too much.

00:08:11.052 --> 00:08:13.718
It was so much so, that Christ had to come on this Earth

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:18.278
and tell people that you better forgive.

00:08:20.647 --> 00:08:23.320
His Advent should have made people more in the centre,

00:08:23.521 --> 00:08:27.084
but it did not. On the contrary all the Christian nations

00:08:27.285 --> 00:08:32.326
went onto right side and we Indians are also following you out.

00:08:32.527 --> 00:08:35.089
So, we are very right-sided people.

00:08:35.290 --> 00:08:42.417
All the Sahaja Yogis today are, 99.9% are right-sided,

00:08:42.618 --> 00:08:46.507
even Indians are.

00:08:46.708 --> 00:08:53.632
The bhakti people are lost; they are not yet here.

00:08:53.833 --> 00:09:02.325
They are another mad people. They are going to this Pandhari temple,

00:09:02.526 --> 00:09:06.059
praying to God, they are in the churches, they are in the temples,

00:09:06.260 --> 00:09:09.471
they are in the mosques, everywhere they are lost.

00:09:09.672 --> 00:09:14.288
So, those who worship the moon, worship the bhakti,

00:09:14.488 --> 00:09:19.951
the so-called love of God, are lost to Sahaja Yoga for the time being.

00:09:20.152 --> 00:09:26.293
More the intellectuals are here.

00:09:26.494 --> 00:09:31.041
Because they really lead others into another.

00:09:31.242 --> 00:09:36.651
They sound more sane than the other.

00:09:36.852 --> 00:09:43.901
But this movement towards the right is overdone.

00:09:44.102 --> 00:09:51.028
So now, to bring Sahaja Yogis to normalcy

00:09:51.228 --> 00:09:55.451
is to bring them to the left side,

00:09:55.652 --> 00:09:58.459
as they are today, as they are today.

00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:02.834
That’s why I took you down to villages, where people are very simple,

00:10:03.035 --> 00:10:07.435
very loving, very affectionate. With right-sided people,

00:10:07.636 --> 00:10:10.886
the brain is so wobbly that you can’t bear any discomfort,

00:10:11.087 --> 00:10:14.768
you can’t bear any discomfort. If there is any discomfort,

00:10:14.969 --> 00:10:16.984
you just can’t bear it

00:10:17.185 --> 00:10:20.193
because all your energies are spent in your brain activity,

00:10:20.394 --> 00:10:23.388
which is useless and thoroughly rubbish, absolutely,

00:10:23.589 --> 00:10:26.882
creating nothing. But it makes you so tired

00:10:27.083 --> 00:10:34.589
that a slight discomfort in the body makes you very, very upset,

00:10:34.790 --> 00:10:42.347
and you can’t bear any physical discomfort.

00:10:42.548 --> 00:10:46.594
Now we Indians are also so enamored by your progress

00:10:46.795 --> 00:10:53.724
that we are also trying to follow your footsteps, and with a double march.

00:10:55.882 --> 00:11:01.717
Under these circumstances, one has to think of those people

00:11:01.918 --> 00:11:09.323
who really love God. There is bhakti, there is devotion.

00:11:10.245 --> 00:11:14.890
They don’t think, they don’t worry;

00:11:15.091 --> 00:11:19.901
they are blindly following God. They know there is God and they said,

00:11:20.102 --> 00:11:23.386
"We will meet God sometime." Whatever mistakes they are creating,

00:11:23.587 --> 00:11:26.979
as you have committed mistakes with your right-sided behavior,

00:11:27.180 --> 00:11:31.682
with the left-side also, they are committing lots of mistakes, no doubt.

00:11:31.883 --> 00:11:36.258
But they are to be brought in.

00:11:36.459 --> 00:11:38.875
You have to meet them, they have to meet you.

00:11:39.076 --> 00:11:44.106
They’ll have a good effect on you, I know they will have.

00:11:45.558 --> 00:11:49.648
To become the moon now, is not so easy, because once

00:11:49.849 --> 00:11:55.990
you have become the sun, rather difficult you have gone a little ahead.

00:11:56.191 --> 00:12:01.341
But to become the moon, you have to develop

00:12:01.542 --> 00:12:09.449
that shraddha, that faith,

00:12:09.650 --> 00:12:13.993
that non-thinking faith,

00:12:14.193 --> 00:12:18.730
that love.

00:12:18.931 --> 00:12:23.578
One may ask, "From where do you start when you sit for meditation?"

00:12:23.779 --> 00:12:26.796
I asked Modi what were the questions.

00:12:26.997 --> 00:12:33.571
"From where to start and where to end?"

00:12:33.772 --> 00:12:41.543
It’s all again technique. Only one technique I would prescribe for you people,

00:12:41.744 --> 00:12:44.381
every group requires a different type of a technique, you see,

00:12:44.582 --> 00:12:47.646
the kind of problems they face, is that you start with your heart

00:12:47.847 --> 00:12:51.238
and end there only.

00:12:51.438 --> 00:12:59.432
It starts from your heart, from your Atma, and ends in your Atma.

00:13:04.811 --> 00:13:14.328
Just give up talking about it, just start feeling your heart;

00:13:14.529 --> 00:13:19.077
just start feeling your heart, opening it out,

00:13:19.278 --> 00:13:24.417
not your mouth so much as your heart.

00:13:28.794 --> 00:13:32.768
What do we do when we love?

00:13:32.976 --> 00:13:37.778
What is the sign and symptom?

00:13:37.979 --> 00:13:46.977
I don’t know, in the West, if that glimpse of love is also there or not.

00:13:47.178 --> 00:13:52.338
But you can see in this country, still.

00:13:53.405 --> 00:13:58.329
Say a mother, if her child is sick.

00:13:58.530 --> 00:14:04.544
I’ve known My own mother, when My brother was very sick

00:14:04.745 --> 00:14:07.786
with typhoid, for twenty-one days and nights,

00:14:07.987 --> 00:14:13.706
she did not sleep a wink, she did not.

00:14:17.986 --> 00:14:26.988
If you have seen that kind of love, then you can understand

00:14:27.189 --> 00:14:33.598
what wonders, she never thought of her comfort,

00:14:33.799 --> 00:14:37.718
nothing, what time she slept, what time she got up.

00:14:37.918 --> 00:14:42.666
She didn’t think of her food, nothing.

00:14:42.867 --> 00:14:49.028
She was just wanting that her son should be alright.

00:14:49.826 --> 00:14:53.168
Now, they said that twenty-one days he has to be sick whatever it is;

00:14:53.368 --> 00:14:57.434
if you try to cure it earlier, it will have a relapse on him

00:14:57.635 --> 00:15:02.125
or some problem .So, twenty-one days, really I’ve seen,

00:15:02.326 --> 00:15:06.778
that she didn’t eat any food.

00:15:08.107 --> 00:15:11.413
She didn’t know what she was eating, anybody who offered her food,

00:15:11.614 --> 00:15:16.512
she would eat little bit and then she would not; she had no desire left,

00:15:16.713 --> 00:15:22.123
but to see that her child is cured.

00:15:26.565 --> 00:15:32.916
How much can we sacrifice for Sahaj Yoga?

00:15:35.358 --> 00:15:40.647
Then I’ll give you another example, which I’ve seen Myself in My childhood.

00:15:40.847 --> 00:15:44.027
Now Indians are very different people,

00:15:44.228 --> 00:15:48.039
but I have seen very great Indians in this country.

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:52.547
When the Britishers were here, they were another type of Britishers also.

00:15:52.748 --> 00:15:57.355
Now you don’t find them anywhere.

00:15:58.137 --> 00:16:00.409
Only thing, that Gandhiji said that you’ll get Swaraj,

00:16:00.610 --> 00:16:05.071
you’ll get independence. Swaraji is actually, swa means your Spirit,

00:16:05.272 --> 00:16:07.534
and the reign of the Spirit.

00:16:07.735 --> 00:16:13.366
But when he said swaraji, he meant political independence.

00:16:13.567 --> 00:16:17.439
And how much people sacrificed for that,

00:16:17.640 --> 00:16:20.634
which they did not enjoy themselves.

00:16:20.835 --> 00:16:27.989
In My own family, My own father who had houses, cars, everything.

00:16:28.190 --> 00:16:35.733
He was a titleholder, he used to get his clothes stitched from England,

00:16:35.934 --> 00:16:38.887
everything was taken away from him, everything that he had,

00:16:39.087 --> 00:16:41.781
everything.

00:16:41.982 --> 00:16:51.227
And we stayed in very ordinary huts on the soil itself.

00:16:51.427 --> 00:16:55.218
There was nothing between us and the Mother Earth.

00:16:55.419 --> 00:16:59.158
But what we felt, that our father was doing it

00:16:59.358 --> 00:17:03.633
for such a great purpose, we were very proud of it.

00:17:03.834 --> 00:17:07.864
We never felt we were sacrificing anything;

00:17:08.065 --> 00:17:10.153
we were very much respected everywhere

00:17:10.354 --> 00:17:15.758
and people offered us free things but we would not accept.

00:17:15.959 --> 00:17:24.378
Such pride that we are doing it, such a great thing,

00:17:24.579 --> 00:17:26.828
for our own country, for our countrymen,

00:17:27.028 --> 00:17:31.469
for such a wider interest.

00:17:38.029 --> 00:17:43.667
In Sahaja Yoga, you don’t have to sacrifice anything.

00:17:43.868 --> 00:17:54.587
Neither money, nor your sleep, which is very important,

00:17:54.788 --> 00:17:58.628
nor your comforts, nothing. Everything you get cheap,

00:17:58.829 --> 00:18:04.324
you see this blessing.

00:18:06.699 --> 00:18:09.448
And what is promised to you is swaraj in the real sense,

00:18:09.648 --> 00:18:15.007
is the domain of your Spirit.

00:18:15.207 --> 00:18:18.278
The liberation of the highest type is promised,

00:18:18.479 --> 00:18:21.489
which you have achieved.

00:18:21.700 --> 00:18:29.495
And sacrifice is zero. You can’t even sacrifice your time.

00:18:30.531 --> 00:18:32.626
On top of that, some people think

00:18:32.827 --> 00:18:38.477
that they are obliging Sahaja Yoga, specially Me.

00:18:38.677 --> 00:18:42.127
It is the absurdity of the whole thing.

00:18:42.327 --> 00:18:45.507
It was not definite also

00:18:45.707 --> 00:18:48.616
that we’ll get independence at that time, nothing definite.

00:18:48.817 --> 00:18:51.736
They went to jail, my mother went to jail 5 times

00:18:51.937 --> 00:18:55.889
with 11 children in the family, only we and our relations, everybody

00:18:56.090 --> 00:19:03.154
staying in the house, all still not educated.

00:19:03.785 --> 00:19:06.154
Now we are other way round,

00:19:06.355 --> 00:19:08.457
today’s politicians are busy making money,

00:19:08.657 --> 00:19:12.017
it is just the other way around system, other way around.

00:19:12.241 --> 00:19:17.030
It is just the other way around. I mean, I can’t understand from where these people have come.

00:19:23.066 --> 00:19:28.927
So, you don’t have to sacrifice anything,

00:19:29.128 --> 00:19:32.144
nothing is to be sacrificed.

00:19:32.345 --> 00:19:42.193
Always, you get an added advantage in this way or that way,

00:19:42.394 --> 00:19:48.666
you are blessed every moment. Count your blessings.

00:19:53.508 --> 00:19:56.984
And then, one should start understanding

00:19:57.185 --> 00:20:02.713
that these blessings are for us to become more loving,

00:20:02.914 --> 00:20:08.008
more generous and sacrificing.

00:20:08.234 --> 00:20:14.802
The idea that we are sacrificing itself is an ego-oriented idea.

00:20:15.004 --> 00:20:22.846
What do you sacrifice? What do we have to sacrifice?

00:20:23.047 --> 00:20:28.425
I mean, supposing I say "I am sacrificing",  it’s nonsense,

00:20:28.626 --> 00:20:31.854
because that’s My nature. I have to jolly well do it,

00:20:32.066 --> 00:20:38.118
can’t help it, I can’t run away. If I run away from you,

00:20:38.319 --> 00:20:40.667
My vibrations will make Me bloat Me like this.

00:20:40.867 --> 00:20:47.271
I won’t be able to even walk. I have to give.

00:20:50.039 --> 00:20:52.298
In the same way, you have to give realization.

00:20:52.499 --> 00:20:56.317
If you think that "In my house, Oh, I do lots of meditation

00:20:56.518 --> 00:21:00.057
Mother, I give exclusively, I am exclusive", finished.

00:21:00.258 --> 00:21:03.097
You cannot go further. You may have your own conception

00:21:03.297 --> 00:21:09.167
that you are going further with it, you are absolutely wrong.

00:21:09.367 --> 00:21:11.467
I allow you to continue with your myths.

00:21:11.667 --> 00:21:16.156
That doesn’t mean that it is true.

00:21:18.958 --> 00:21:24.868
People ask Me, "How many times should we attend the program?

00:21:25.087 --> 00:21:30.587
How many times should we meditate?"

00:21:31.683 --> 00:21:35.940
Every moment.

00:21:36.141 --> 00:21:42.571
You have to take responsibility of Sahaja Yoga now.

00:21:42.772 --> 00:21:47.627
You have to become responsible for it in your own way.

00:21:47.837 --> 00:21:53.678
You have to do it because you are doing it for the greater good.

00:21:53.878 --> 00:21:56.339
The more you think of the greater good it is doing,

00:21:56.540 --> 00:22:00.532
the better it would be for you.

00:22:00.733 --> 00:22:06.235
All these are the qualities of the left side, heart, the Atma.

00:22:06.436 --> 00:22:13.287
Atma is all the time giving, it cannot receive.

00:22:13.488 --> 00:22:19.297
That is why it is untarnishable, it is unsurmountable.

00:22:19.498 --> 00:22:23.589
Who can surmount it? Because it is the king of itself.

00:22:23.790 --> 00:22:27.816
Nobody can dominate, nothing; no material wealth,

00:22:28.017 --> 00:22:33.745
nothing can dominate it, it is above.

00:22:35.182 --> 00:22:39.597
So, to get to subtler life, "Take to spiritual life," they say.

00:22:39.797 --> 00:22:42.408
But spiritual life means what? They don’t understand.

00:22:42.625 --> 00:22:48.366
And ‘spirit’ in English language is such a misnomer

00:22:48.567 --> 00:22:51.527
that for three things they use one word ‘spirit’, can you imagine?

00:22:51.728 --> 00:22:57.166
For the dead, for the spirit that they drink, and the Spirit that,

00:22:57.367 --> 00:23:02.275
so called, exists within them.

00:23:03.087 --> 00:23:07.987
It is absurd isn’t it, to give such a name one name to the three things,

00:23:08.187 --> 00:23:12.838
which are absolutely contradicting each other?

00:23:13.038 --> 00:23:21.010
So, to get to subtler life, one has to get to the Spirit,

00:23:21.211 --> 00:23:24.104
to the subtleties of everything.

00:23:24.305 --> 00:23:28.597
Now, I’ll give you a concrete example.

00:23:28.798 --> 00:23:34.632
You need not pull your ears for that, see to the subtleness.

00:23:34.833 --> 00:23:45.106
In Pune, people wanted to give you some presents.

00:23:46.278 --> 00:23:50.428
They said, "What should we give?" I said, "Give them

00:23:50.629 --> 00:23:55.998
the soil of Maharashtra."

00:23:56.199 --> 00:24:02.178
Every particle is vibrated here – clay of Maharashtra.

00:24:02.378 --> 00:24:14.025
Last time if you remember, they gave you a incense-burning

00:24:14.225 --> 00:24:17.147
what we call Dhupat in Marathi. I don’t know what you call in English,

00:24:17.347 --> 00:24:20.740
there is no name for such a thing but you know what they gave you.

00:24:20.941 --> 00:24:24.248
This time I said give some symbolic and I chose that for you.

00:24:24.449 --> 00:24:27.908
I wanted to see your reactions.

00:24:28.109 --> 00:24:32.121
What reactions you will have. It was chosen with a purpose.

00:24:32.322 --> 00:24:35.800
It is a very important thing you are taking with you.

00:24:36.001 --> 00:24:45.879
Is a very important thing, is vibrated clay from Maharashta.

00:24:47.402 --> 00:24:49.939
It’s a very great thing. Though in Pune,

00:24:50.140 --> 00:24:53.667
people are very miserly, agreed;

00:24:53.867 --> 00:24:57.587
they always make a mess of many things, agreed;

00:24:57.788 --> 00:25:08.083
but the soil is vibrated, is punyas there.

00:25:09.763 --> 00:25:13.530
And out of that soil, I wanted to find out something

00:25:13.731 --> 00:25:21.145
that would be symbolic. I myself went before the Puja to select it.

00:25:22.574 --> 00:25:28.313
Now, what you have made out of it is not so satisfactory.

00:25:29.254 --> 00:25:33.902
That is the most important thing, you are taking from here.

00:25:35.527 --> 00:25:41.690
All other things are of utility of a very gross nature.

00:25:43.955 --> 00:25:46.448
You may try;

00:25:46.648 --> 00:25:52.257
you can put a plant in it which will give vibrations.

00:25:53.382 --> 00:25:57.657
So, I was told that they were asked to send it by ship.

00:25:57.857 --> 00:26:02.727
It is very wrong. But if I give you a silver thing, you will carry it with you.

00:26:02.928 --> 00:26:07.467
Will you send it by ship?

00:26:11.507 --> 00:26:13.919
Nothing to pull your ears for.

00:26:14.120 --> 00:26:17.521
But to get to subtler things is to understand

00:26:17.768 --> 00:26:27.251
the subtler values of everything.

00:26:28.898 --> 00:26:34.413
It cannot be weighed or understood through money.

00:26:35.202 --> 00:26:38.897
Because in the West, you know, people buy everything as an investment,

00:26:39.098 --> 00:26:41.680
everything. I don’t know how they don’t buy even their nose

00:26:41.880 --> 00:26:44.213
for an investment.

00:26:44.414 --> 00:26:46.995
Everything, they must be standardized,

00:26:47.196 --> 00:26:52.275
because it should have a resale value. I mean, imagine to have everything

00:26:52.475 --> 00:26:59.428
which is saleable means there is no feeling for that thing.

00:26:59.628 --> 00:27:02.340
They would buy even a certificate the same way;

00:27:02.541 --> 00:27:05.881
even the bed they sleep in, everything should be saleable,

00:27:06.082 --> 00:27:10.191
resalable, I mean.

00:27:11.166 --> 00:27:19.486
And this is the curse of that country. In this country, it is not so.

00:27:19.687 --> 00:27:22.799
For them, silver need not be so much standardized

00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:25.947
and gold need not be so much standardized.

00:27:26.148 --> 00:27:30.405
Gold, they may like to have pure gold because it is good for vibrations.

00:27:30.606 --> 00:27:34.524
But such standardization in these things, it’s all right

00:27:34.725 --> 00:27:38.127
for, say, bathroom pipes you should have standard;

00:27:38.327 --> 00:27:43.853
but for these small, small things there should be no standardization.

00:27:44.054 --> 00:27:48.567
Because they do not feel the vibrations.

00:27:48.768 --> 00:27:55.037
If you start understanding things that have vibrations,

00:27:55.237 --> 00:27:59.439
then you will be amazed that the things, that they look so insipid,

00:27:59.640 --> 00:28:03.122
so useless, not resalable at all

00:28:03.323 --> 00:28:07.317
you can say worthless, you can call it from all

00:28:07.518 --> 00:28:13.871
our standards absolutely worthless could be so much useful.

00:28:14.072 --> 00:28:16.510
Like one hair of Mohammed sahib, imagine ,

00:28:16.711 --> 00:28:20.139
one hair of Mohammed sahib;

00:28:20.340 --> 00:28:22.047
shroud of Christ,

00:28:22.248 --> 00:28:24.804
shroud of Christ, but that also they are selling now,

00:28:25.004 --> 00:28:28.326
they are making money out of that also. I mean, thanks to these Western people,

00:28:28.527 --> 00:28:32.617
everything is saleable.

00:28:35.840 --> 00:28:42.771
So, once you start going to the subtler side of the physical things,

00:28:42.972 --> 00:28:49.798
not only aesthetics, aesthetics are also saleable,

00:28:49.998 --> 00:28:57.037
but things that cannot be sold, you cannot sell your spirit.

00:28:57.237 --> 00:29:03.292
They should be the most precious things for you,

00:29:03.493 --> 00:29:08.293
which is the most precious energy for you.

00:29:08.494 --> 00:29:13.368
Our values are changed. We are different people.

00:29:13.569 --> 00:29:20.670
Which is the most precious energy for us? Is the living energy.

00:29:20.871 --> 00:29:26.448
The synthesized energy of all the energies is the living energy.

00:29:26.648 --> 00:29:32.310
But we believe in money energy or destructive energies

00:29:32.511 --> 00:29:38.680
or atomic energies, electrical energies, now petrol energies

00:29:38.881 --> 00:29:42.366
and all these points will be hit

00:29:42.567 --> 00:29:48.009
to understand that you have to do without them.

00:29:48.210 --> 00:29:57.987
So the greatest thing for a Sahaja Yogi is the living energy,

00:29:58.187 --> 00:30:02.341
and the sign of living energy is that it grows

00:30:02.542 --> 00:30:07.474
and discards all that is useless for it.

00:30:07.675 --> 00:30:10.877
It knows how to work it out.

00:30:11.078 --> 00:30:15.572
In the same way, a Sahaja Yogi should know what is important,

00:30:15.773 --> 00:30:22.414
what is unimportant. You are judged every moment, naturally,

00:30:22.615 --> 00:30:30.905
because you have entered into the judgment of God.

00:30:34.882 --> 00:30:44.146
This understanding of becoming subtler comes through love.

00:30:50.907 --> 00:31:00.549
What is love, is hard to describe. You can only enjoy it.

00:31:00.750 --> 00:31:05.477
I enjoy it, when a villager brings something so simple,

00:31:05.677 --> 00:31:09.070
and makes Me eat that.

00:31:09.271 --> 00:31:16.967
Like the small little fruits called ber were given to Shri Rama.

00:31:17.167 --> 00:31:21.290
Shri Rama Himself was born on the right side.

00:31:21.491 --> 00:31:24.006
Great example for all of you is Shri Rama

00:31:24.207 --> 00:31:28.772
who was on the right side, who works the right side.

00:31:28.989 --> 00:31:34.085
When He was born and He was a child, He is a Suryavanshi,

00:31:34.286 --> 00:31:38.720
He is the son of Surya. I mean Surya,

00:31:38.920 --> 00:31:42.389
everything comes from the Sun to Him.

00:31:42.590 --> 00:31:46.277
When He was born and was a little child,

00:31:46.477 --> 00:31:52.129
He asked His mother that "I would like to have the Moon."

00:31:52.329 --> 00:31:56.939
He started crying, and nobody knew how to satisfy.

00:31:57.140 --> 00:32:02.467
He said "I want to have the Moon." They gave Him many toys, He’d throw away.

00:32:02.667 --> 00:32:06.085
They said, "What a child it is, funny thing.

00:32:06.286 --> 00:32:12.161
He wants to have the moon, now how to get Him the moon?"

00:32:14.777 --> 00:32:16.826
They did not know how to solve the problem.

00:32:17.027 --> 00:32:19.654
He said, "Somehow you get Me the moon. I don’t want to eat or anything,

00:32:19.855 --> 00:32:24.211
I want to have the moon." Here the moon represents the Atma,

00:32:24.411 --> 00:32:29.428
the cooling capacity.

00:32:29.628 --> 00:32:32.722
He asked for the moon.

00:32:32.923 --> 00:32:38.291
You are all on the right side, so ask for the moon.

00:32:38.491 --> 00:32:43.477
Ask for the Spirit. And they didn’t know how to satisfy this Shri Rama,

00:32:43.677 --> 00:32:48.311
who was the incarnation of Shri Vishnu,

00:32:48.512 --> 00:32:53.273
asking for the moon of all the things,

00:32:53.474 --> 00:32:57.307
not for anything else. What is so important?

00:32:57.508 --> 00:33:04.558
So, the mother has always a intuition.

00:33:04.758 --> 00:33:08.987
She brought a… it’s a, it’s a maya, it is a beautiful drama.

00:33:09.187 --> 00:33:12.487
She brought a mirror and showed Him the moon in the mirror.

00:33:12.687 --> 00:33:17.312
He said, "Now you can get the moon here."

00:33:17.513 --> 00:33:22.768
So sweet. And He was satisfied.

00:33:22.969 --> 00:33:26.726
Even the reflection of that can satisfy.

00:33:26.927 --> 00:33:35.597
You are like the mirrors and I want to see the reflection of moon in you.

00:33:36.738 --> 00:33:45.487
The love we talk of is to be subtler.

00:33:45.687 --> 00:33:52.703
It becomes really subtler when you really enjoy.

00:33:53.978 --> 00:34:02.304
Like giving something to someone is one of the ways of judging it.

00:34:02.505 --> 00:34:10.622
When you start to enjoy giving – not taking, just giving –

00:34:10.823 --> 00:34:15.277
then you should know on material level you have felt,

00:34:15.477 --> 00:34:20.930
you have touched that shore of subtlety on material level only.

00:34:23.155 --> 00:34:29.576
On emotional level you can,  in India,

00:34:29.777 --> 00:34:33.318
I mean, everybody loves their children, I mean it’s a bit too much,

00:34:33.519 --> 00:34:36.177
going too far. I mean, they can even sell their country

00:34:36.378 --> 00:34:38.729
in the name of their children.

00:34:38.930 --> 00:34:42.812
It is going too far, their wives, I mean, it is a trip,

00:34:43.013 --> 00:34:49.047
their husbands, is a bit too much. The other side is in the West,

00:34:49.248 --> 00:34:54.328
where they don’t believe in all this nonsensical love.

00:34:56.243 --> 00:35:06.877
In between, the subtlety of love is that love a person,

00:35:07.078 --> 00:35:13.891
not with any reasoning, with any way of gain

00:35:14.092 --> 00:35:23.548
or any relationship whatsoever, just emit love.

00:35:26.348 --> 00:35:30.520
Whether you are recognized or not,

00:35:30.721 --> 00:35:34.778
just emit love is the subtler way of loving.

00:35:34.986 --> 00:35:42.132
That love cures people,

00:35:42.333 --> 00:35:46.602
that love comforts,

00:35:46.803 --> 00:35:50.147
that’s the comforting side, it comforts.

00:35:50.347 --> 00:35:54.184
To begin with, we should see to the comforts of others.

00:35:54.385 --> 00:35:59.087
Self-indulgence is against that love.

00:36:00.727 --> 00:36:05.321
People would like to make My bed, all right.

00:36:05.587 --> 00:36:10.509
They love Me I know. But it must permeate to others.

00:36:10.710 --> 00:36:15.879
They love Me and second they love themselves, that’s no good.

00:36:16.080 --> 00:36:18.716
Between Me and them there is a big gap.

00:36:18.917 --> 00:36:25.788
All that is filled by others. Who are the others? Are the Sahaja Yogis.

00:36:25.988 --> 00:36:29.157
We would never make a bed of another Sahaja Yogi,

00:36:29.357 --> 00:36:34.988
out of love also, very difficult, it’s too much.

00:36:35.188 --> 00:36:38.049
But to find out the faults with other Sahaja Yogis,

00:36:38.250 --> 00:36:41.703
"You got up very early, you opened the tap bit loudly,

00:36:41.904 --> 00:36:46.783
I couldn’t sleep." This is a very common complaint.

00:36:46.984 --> 00:36:52.809
"They banged the door early in the morning, they made a noise."

00:36:53.010 --> 00:36:59.518
Because your brains are out now, with thinking.

00:36:59.719 --> 00:37:02.299
You are so much strained here

00:37:02.500 --> 00:37:05.990
that you can’t bear any sounds anywhere.

00:37:06.191 --> 00:37:13.066
I mean, people can only live in a churchyard happily I think,

00:37:13.267 --> 00:37:16.123
if that is the situation.

00:37:16.331 --> 00:37:19.280
While in India, you see, we don’t mind any kind of noise

00:37:19.481 --> 00:37:21.795
anywhere. I mean, as it is, wherever I have stayed,

00:37:21.996 --> 00:37:26.387
there has been a railway station around.

00:37:26.838 --> 00:37:29.833
We could hear all the shunting, everything going on

00:37:30.034 --> 00:37:34.877
and I enjoyed really all that.

00:37:36.684 --> 00:37:42.848
So, when we start comforting others,

00:37:43.048 --> 00:37:49.598
to give comfort to their physical body, to their mental body,

00:37:49.798 --> 00:37:54.947
that is also a very farfetched thing. Because to say comforting things,

00:37:55.147 --> 00:37:59.095
to say beautiful things to others, is regarded I don’t know what.

00:37:59.296 --> 00:38:03.845
In the West it is very hard to find people who can find out words

00:38:04.046 --> 00:38:07.489
to say sweet things to others. Same in India,

00:38:07.690 --> 00:38:11.893
specially in Maharashtra. Marathi language can be very harsh.

00:38:12.097 --> 00:38:18.526
[Marathi]

00:38:20.523 --> 00:38:24.749
[Marathi]

00:38:26.968 --> 00:38:29.960
Speak sweet words,

00:38:30.161 --> 00:38:35.697
say something sweet, be kind and nice.

00:38:35.897 --> 00:38:43.618
It is so nice to hear that you are sweet to each other.

00:38:43.818 --> 00:38:46.745
When people come and tell Me that

00:38:46.946 --> 00:38:56.306
"Such and such Sahaja Yogi came and comforted me, and was very kind",

00:38:56.507 --> 00:39:01.204
I really feel Sahaja Yoga is working in a big way.

00:39:01.405 --> 00:39:04.219
I feel it in a very big way. You may have

00:39:04.420 --> 00:39:09.615
thousands of them, what is it? There is no quality there.

00:39:10.154 --> 00:39:12.672
Try to mold your Vishuddhi in a proper way,

00:39:12.873 --> 00:39:17.768
otherwise you will have Vishuddhi troubles, I must say.

00:39:17.968 --> 00:39:22.724
Try to use language which is extremely sweet.

00:39:22.925 --> 00:39:25.334
It doesn’t mean hypocrisy.

00:39:25.535 --> 00:39:29.907
No, you are great inside, you want to love.

00:39:30.107 --> 00:39:32.823
But there is a barrier of your ego.

00:39:33.024 --> 00:39:36.081
When your light of love passes through that ego,

00:39:36.282 --> 00:39:40.887
It gets falsified, it gets ruined, it gets spoilt

00:39:41.088 --> 00:39:46.881
and then you say harsh words to others.

00:39:52.558 --> 00:39:59.105
Try to be sweet, through your Vishuddhi Chakra.

00:40:00.208 --> 00:40:01.359
Once you start doing that,

00:40:01.567 --> 00:40:04.790
you will develop your witness state very well.

00:40:05.058 --> 00:40:07.894
Because, first of all, you witness yourself, which is trying to be nasty

00:40:08.095 --> 00:40:11.472
to others and enjoy that nastiness.

00:40:11.673 --> 00:40:15.835
There is a Hitler sitting in your Vishuddhi.

00:40:17.544 --> 00:40:22.966
And that Hitler you start seeing, "All right, Mr. Hitler."

00:40:25.213 --> 00:40:33.739
It wants to say something very harsh, you see, because that appeals to your ego,

00:40:33.940 --> 00:40:37.587
which we call as intelligence. You see our misidentifications are, you see,

00:40:37.788 --> 00:40:41.128
You are very intelligent, very sharp."

00:40:41.329 --> 00:40:46.155
That’s only ego, one of the agents of ego.

00:40:47.092 --> 00:40:52.616
So try to be sweet in your tongue.

00:40:52.817 --> 00:40:56.131
It is very easy to make fun of people for small things here and there,

00:40:56.332 --> 00:41:02.183
anything making easy. [Marathi]

00:41:06.465 --> 00:41:09.818
In Maharashtra, people are known for such a thing

00:41:10.018 --> 00:41:13.558
how to make fun of everyone.

00:41:13.758 --> 00:41:17.742
But when we start making fun of others, we also become

00:41:17.943 --> 00:41:21.689
a target of fun.

00:41:21.890 --> 00:41:24.470
English also are like that, very much.

00:41:24.671 --> 00:41:32.088
Everyone, I should say, but English are quite special

00:41:32.288 --> 00:41:39.388
to make fun of everyone. Of course, Sahaja Yogis are now realizing.

00:41:39.589 --> 00:41:42.998
Everyone has their own style of dealing with things.

00:41:43.198 --> 00:41:49.933
Like, I would say Americans are, they have no respect of themselves,

00:41:50.134 --> 00:41:54.048
no respect for themselves. I mean, they have no respect at all,

00:41:54.249 --> 00:41:57.204
for themselves or anybody else’s life or for anyone,

00:41:57.405 --> 00:42:01.897
they have no respect of any kind.

00:42:05.255 --> 00:42:10.530
Indians are hypocritical, very hypocritical people.

00:42:10.731 --> 00:42:13.929
Like that, everybody has problem. Now you have become Sahaja Yogis,

00:42:14.130 --> 00:42:17.163
you are no more English, Indians, Americans, nothing.

00:42:17.364 --> 00:42:20.280
You are Sahaja Yogis. You belong to a great,

00:42:20.481 --> 00:42:24.131
very, very great organization of God.

00:42:24.332 --> 00:42:27.997
And Sahaja Yoga is the place where you have to learn,

00:42:28.198 --> 00:42:37.360
in every way. For Indians have to learn how to be honest

00:42:37.561 --> 00:42:40.847
and English have to learn how to love.

00:42:41.048 --> 00:42:46.462
Americans have to learn how to be self-respecting.

00:42:47.110 --> 00:42:51.726
All of us have to learn, give up what we had, our identifications,

00:42:51.927 --> 00:42:56.054
and have to become subtler and universal

00:42:56.255 --> 00:43:01.175
and people of such values that anybody who sees will say

00:43:01.376 --> 00:43:08.358
that in America Mother has created Abraham Lincolns,

00:43:08.558 --> 00:43:15.172
in Russia Tolstoys, in Maharashtra Shivajis.

00:43:16.672 --> 00:43:21.738
I’m too ambitious, I should say,

00:43:21.938 --> 00:43:26.427
but I see reality in you and reality in Myself.

00:43:26.627 --> 00:43:30.723
On that basis, I say, one has to create

00:43:30.924 --> 00:43:35.541
people of that special quality which they have sterling qualities,

00:43:35.742 --> 00:43:44.187
sterling qualities, spiritual qualities which are so subtle, so beautiful,

00:43:44.387 --> 00:43:49.913
so sweet, so understanding. And still, just like steel,

00:43:50.114 --> 00:43:57.792
nobody can budge them from their own principles, tatwas.

00:44:00.587 --> 00:44:04.242
That is what it is, so simple as that.

00:44:04.443 --> 00:44:08.594
And then you start enjoying your love, enjoying your virtues,

00:44:08.795 --> 00:44:14.747
enjoying everything and having compassion for others.

00:44:14.948 --> 00:44:21.165
Then you don’t catch; you catch because you don’t have compassion.

00:44:21.366 --> 00:44:24.358
In compassion you’ll never catch, never.

00:44:24.559 --> 00:44:26.632
A mother never gets a disease from her child.

00:44:26.833 --> 00:44:32.612
She never gets a disease from her child, it’s a fact.

00:44:35.088 --> 00:44:40.038
Child may be a tuberculosis patient or could be any patient,

00:44:40.238 --> 00:44:49.137
she never catches because she loves.

00:44:49.337 --> 00:44:54.539
In the same way, when you really love, you’ll never catch anything.

00:44:54.740 --> 00:44:56.820
Then what is the question of what is to clear, where to clear,

00:44:57.021 --> 00:45:01.460
what to do, what does it matter? You are just flowing your heart.

00:45:01.661 --> 00:45:05.000
At this moment, My children, My Sahaja Yogis

00:45:05.201 --> 00:45:10.928
are at that level that they can completely open their heart

00:45:11.129 --> 00:45:15.598
without any fear.

00:45:17.458 --> 00:45:19.779
It’s a very different stage you have reached now;

00:45:19.980 --> 00:45:23.588
you are at a different stage. Just assume your powers.

00:45:23.788 --> 00:45:30.804
Know that you are that. Just open your heart.

00:45:31.030 --> 00:45:33.999
Like, the other day I saw somebody, he was caught up very badly

00:45:34.200 --> 00:45:37.880
from all the sides, not Sahaja Yogi, somebody else. And I asked him,

00:45:38.081 --> 00:45:42.512
"How did you manage to get so many bhoots into yourself?"

00:45:42.713 --> 00:45:45.645
Every, every guru you name, he is there.

00:45:45.846 --> 00:45:51.256
I said, "How did you manage?" He said, "I have a very open heart."

00:45:52.301 --> 00:45:55.644
"Oh God," I said.

00:45:56.941 --> 00:46:00.050
I said, "It’s like an open window in a dirty place.

00:46:00.251 --> 00:46:07.057
You get every smell, every mosquitoes and bugs walking into it."

00:46:12.469 --> 00:46:20.513
So, the fear of opening your heart to that extent, comes from that, from that experience.

00:46:20.714 --> 00:46:26.985
But now, you are at such a stage that, open your heart.

00:46:28.618 --> 00:46:33.608
There should be no fear; there will be no problem,

00:46:33.808 --> 00:46:38.539
material problems are not difficult to be solved.

00:46:38.740 --> 00:46:44.506
Like, somebody was taking My photograph

00:46:44.707 --> 00:46:48.326
which was in a silver frame and she was rather worry,

00:46:48.527 --> 00:46:52.716
because the customs may stop her not taking.

00:46:52.917 --> 00:46:57.534
Of course, photograph they can’t stop, but maybe the silver frame.

00:46:59.096 --> 00:47:06.198
And this gentleman told Me that he was taking it

00:47:06.399 --> 00:47:09.860
with him with a frame, silver frame and he thought people will object.

00:47:10.061 --> 00:47:13.039
But as soon as they saw the photograph they said namaskar to the photograph,

00:47:13.240 --> 00:47:18.209
forgot about the frame.

00:47:24.067 --> 00:47:27.170
So many problems can be solved,

00:47:27.371 --> 00:47:34.505
material problems is so simple to be solved, so simple.

00:47:36.872 --> 00:47:41.731
Is the easiest to be solved, physical problems also.

00:47:41.932 --> 00:47:45.613
I have known of some Sahaja Yogis who have been in Sahaja Yoga

00:47:45.814 --> 00:47:48.288
six, seven years. But still they are frightened about their body,

00:47:48.488 --> 00:47:53.715
their physical body, the troubles they have had and this and that.

00:47:53.916 --> 00:47:57.799
If they can just leave that fear, they’ll get out of it.

00:47:58.000 --> 00:48:01.298
It is such a vicious circle built in.

00:48:01.498 --> 00:48:05.229
And the same thing works out with our open heart surgery,

00:48:05.430 --> 00:48:09.844
as we call it. We are afraid that our heart will be again

00:48:10.045 --> 00:48:14.500
caught up into nonsensical things, so we don’t want to open our heart.

00:48:14.701 --> 00:48:20.256
That fear I can understand. But now you are Sahaja Yogis, finished.

00:48:20.457 --> 00:48:24.903
Ask all these people to get lost.

00:48:25.104 --> 00:48:30.409
All these fears, you should ask them to get lost.

00:48:33.057 --> 00:48:38.071
When you discover that you are the Spirit,

00:48:38.272 --> 00:48:42.988
you are that powerful Spirit, just try to steady.

00:48:43.188 --> 00:48:48.272
How it feels happy. It’s very simple.

00:48:48.473 --> 00:48:51.186
When do you feel really happy? Is when you give something,

00:48:51.387 --> 00:48:55.715
not to Mataji only. To Me you are, I know.

00:48:55.916 --> 00:49:00.848
If I take something from you, you will feel very happy about it, I know.

00:49:01.049 --> 00:49:08.117
But to somebody else; give some love, comfort.

00:49:08.317 --> 00:49:17.647
What a great power this voice and this vani has,

00:49:17.847 --> 00:49:23.511
that you can comfort others by saying good things.

00:49:23.712 --> 00:49:26.859
Can you imagine what a power God has given you?

00:49:27.060 --> 00:49:32.556
Without spending a single pie, you can comfort others,

00:49:32.757 --> 00:49:36.156
only by saying good things. If you say a mantra,

00:49:36.357 --> 00:49:39.523
you’ll comfort them more in a subtle way.

00:49:39.724 --> 00:49:47.318
If you instill love of God within them, it is even greater.

00:49:47.518 --> 00:49:57.621
And the joy of that is so much because the Spirit is joy.

00:49:57.822 --> 00:50:02.023
The more you open it out, the more light comes in,

00:50:02.224 --> 00:50:05.711
more it works out.

00:50:05.912 --> 00:50:08.685
So give up that fear

00:50:08.886 --> 00:50:12.233
which is placed within you in your experiences.

00:50:12.434 --> 00:50:16.139
Now, this is a new experience of a new life,

00:50:16.340 --> 00:50:19.597
where your energy comes from the Spirit,

00:50:19.829 --> 00:50:23.557
which is love. In one word it is love.

00:50:23.758 --> 00:50:31.996
And in three words, it is truth, it is attention and it is joy.

00:50:32.196 --> 00:50:40.877
All put together it is love. When you mix them up, it becomes love.

00:50:41.077 --> 00:50:46.453
And that is what you have, it’s the great power of love.

00:50:46.654 --> 00:50:49.242
Through your attention, you love others,

00:50:49.443 --> 00:50:52.432
even attention is sufficient.

00:50:52.648 --> 00:50:56.881
To be attentive. See, I needed a handkerchief, all right.

00:50:57.082 --> 00:51:00.634
That’s true. I needed a handkerchief.

00:51:00.835 --> 00:51:05.191
I forgot. I mean, usually I forget all these things.

00:51:05.392 --> 00:51:11.044
Then they felt the need, "Mother needs just a handkerchief."

00:51:11.245 --> 00:51:18.145
They brought the handkerchief; a very simple action, you know,

00:51:18.346 --> 00:51:22.918
but the attention is on Me.

00:51:23.119 --> 00:51:28.935
With little things like handkerchie, you can comfort people.

00:51:29.136 --> 00:51:33.374
For a Sahaja Yogi, even to give a handkerchief, itself is so vibrated,

00:51:33.575 --> 00:51:35.835
itself is.

00:51:36.036 --> 00:51:39.999
To win over other people is also this way:

00:51:40.200 --> 00:51:45.548
to be kind to them, to give them.

00:51:45.748 --> 00:51:51.507
But to give them realization is the highest thing.

00:51:53.593 --> 00:51:56.011
Now, when you become subtler and subtler,

00:51:56.212 --> 00:52:01.238
you will see that you will not have sympathies with people

00:52:01.439 --> 00:52:08.759
who are afflicted, not sympathies, but you will have love for them.

00:52:08.960 --> 00:52:14.491
There is a big difference between sympathy and love.

00:52:14.692 --> 00:52:17.160
When you have sympathy means what?

00:52:17.361 --> 00:52:19.919
You share pathos.

00:52:20.120 --> 00:52:23.719
Pathos. If you want to share pathos, share.

00:52:23.920 --> 00:52:28.298
Very good idea is to share pathos.

00:52:28.498 --> 00:52:34.878
But if you want to share joy,

00:52:35.079 --> 00:52:38.437
you will not have sympathy, you’ll have love.

00:52:38.637 --> 00:52:42.131
You want to share your joy of your Spirit with another person,

00:52:42.332 --> 00:52:45.028
so you may talk to that person in a way

00:52:45.229 --> 00:52:49.403
that may not look so much pleasing and falling at his feet,

00:52:49.604 --> 00:52:53.278
and – you see, this is the work of politicians or business people,

00:52:53.479 --> 00:52:57.087
not yours. You are not seeking any business out of them;

00:52:57.288 --> 00:53:00.494
you want them to come to realization.

00:53:00.695 --> 00:53:08.746
So, you have to say things which are wrong very firmly.

00:53:08.947 --> 00:53:11.240
With a real firm hand you have to say,

00:53:11.441 --> 00:53:15.011
"This is absolutely wrong, absurd."

00:53:15.212 --> 00:53:18.051
You have to convince on that point, on that if you go on saying like this,

00:53:18.252 --> 00:53:20.951
like that, it will never go into their heads because they are bhoots

00:53:21.151 --> 00:53:24.613
and you have to hit them hard.

00:53:24.813 --> 00:53:27.436
That is also love.

00:53:27.636 --> 00:53:36.187
So, love is the strongest thing and the sweetest thing.

00:53:36.388 --> 00:53:39.377
Is such a beautiful combination

00:53:39.577 --> 00:53:46.581
and the one who has the wisdom, that subtler wisdom, can only achieve it.

00:53:46.782 --> 00:53:50.357
Now again the mind will work, "How to do it?"

00:53:50.558 --> 00:53:57.258
So, I think all of you should put this word "how" into the sea.

00:54:00.703 --> 00:54:03.296
There is another very good word in English language,

00:54:03.497 --> 00:54:08.101
which you should use: "why not!"

00:54:13.668 --> 00:54:19.756
That’s the way you can assure yourself, ascertain yourself,

00:54:19.957 --> 00:54:27.329
work it out that way into complete blessing of God.

00:54:27.530 --> 00:54:31.689
You have to just pass those blessings to others, that’s all.

00:54:31.890 --> 00:54:39.633
Nothing more is to be done, just pass that light to others.

00:54:39.834 --> 00:54:45.047
For that, what you need is a man

00:54:45.248 --> 00:54:50.678
who has accepted love as his career,

00:54:50.879 --> 00:54:53.626
a man who worships love,

00:54:53.827 --> 00:55:02.332
a person who thinks love is above all.

00:55:02.886 --> 00:55:10.878
So today, to save the Surya from grahana,

00:55:11.079 --> 00:55:16.528
we extend our love to Him

00:55:16.728 --> 00:55:22.483
and ask Him to create love

00:55:22.684 --> 00:55:28.489
in the hearts of people who worship Him.

00:55:29.538 --> 00:55:37.463
Those who worship Surya, must know that Christ resides in that center,

00:55:37.664 --> 00:55:42.026
who was nothing but love. All His life He loved.

00:55:42.227 --> 00:55:45.251
He sacrificed Himself,

00:55:45.452 --> 00:55:51.126
because He loved you so much that He wanted

00:55:51.327 --> 00:55:54.768
you all to get into the kingdom of God.

00:55:54.968 --> 00:56:02.819
He sacrificed Himself at the altar of God’s forbidden territories.

00:56:03.020 --> 00:56:08.927
He made it possible for you to go there by sucking your ego and superego.

00:56:09.127 --> 00:56:13.676
He is the messenger of love who was born on the Surya.

00:56:13.877 --> 00:56:20.147
So, to do the greatest justice to Surya is to decide today

00:56:20.347 --> 00:56:33.123
that you will take up love as your worshipping, as your Puja.

00:56:33.912 --> 00:56:39.068
May God bless you all!

00:56:39.268 --> 00:56:41.966
Any questions?

00:56:44.357 --> 00:56:45.195
Yes.

00:56:45.396 --> 00:56:50.349
Q: What about the Australians, Mother?

00:57:02.651 --> 00:57:13.356
They are rather safe people, but they have to be deeper.

00:57:14.137 --> 00:57:17.807
They still are under a shock, I would say,

00:57:18.008 --> 00:57:21.142
that they think that they are away from the whole world,

00:57:21.343 --> 00:57:28.437
separated and they have to get into deeper ways of life.

00:57:28.638 --> 00:57:36.458
They are loving people compared to other countries, no doubt,

00:57:36.675 --> 00:57:42.081
but one has to go deep down, deep down.

00:57:42.282 --> 00:57:47.862
You have to be very deep, very deep.

00:57:48.063 --> 00:57:50.658
You should know that Australia was once placed

00:57:50.859 --> 00:57:55.880
between Africa and India.

00:57:56.081 --> 00:57:59.515
I am going to Perth, the African side

00:57:59.716 --> 00:58:03.873
and then to Indian side which is Sydney and all these places.

00:58:04.074 --> 00:58:08.572
But you must not be satisfied

00:58:08.773 --> 00:58:11.919
with all the Western culture you have imbibed, the Western things you have,

00:58:12.120 --> 00:58:17.154
you are not in the West, you are in the East.

00:58:17.355 --> 00:58:20.224
Because you are not on the West, if you try to follow them,

00:58:20.425 --> 00:58:23.957
it’s just mimicry, it’s very superficial.

00:58:24.158 --> 00:58:27.068
So, not the Sahaja Yogis I am saying, but otherwise,

00:58:27.269 --> 00:58:31.282
the people, Australians are very superficial people.

00:58:31.483 --> 00:58:35.813
They drink much more than the Scotland people drink,

00:58:36.014 --> 00:58:39.595
I mean in every way, they are very, very too much,

00:58:39.796 --> 00:58:43.040
I woud say, and that’s how they are wrong.

00:58:43.241 --> 00:58:50.148
So they have to get to the subtler side by developing

00:58:50.349 --> 00:58:54.068
deeper understanding into the aesthetics of life,

00:58:54.269 --> 00:59:01.771
into the beauties of life, the beauties of language, all right?

00:59:01.972 --> 00:59:08.808
This is how if they go about, it would be wonderful place.

00:59:09.009 --> 00:59:15.241
English are very developed that way. They have lots of beauties,

00:59:15.442 --> 00:59:20.881
understanding of beauties, this thing, that thing. But they have become, sort of,

00:59:21.082 --> 00:59:25.488
you see, they think they are the wisest of all, they are stupid.

00:59:25.688 --> 00:59:28.763
And they think they are the wisest, you see

00:59:28.974 --> 00:59:33.843
Australians, on the whole do not think they are the wisest,

00:59:34.044 --> 00:59:37.338
but they should know they can become the wisest.

00:59:37.538 --> 00:59:40.753
Because you live on superficial level, you see you think that

00:59:40.954 --> 00:59:44.659
everything should be tackled on superficial level, that’s not the point.

00:59:44.860 --> 00:59:47.813
You can be the wisest. As English could be, you could be,

00:59:48.014 --> 00:59:52.108
anybody could be.

00:59:52.655 --> 00:59:58.368
And as it is the Mooladhara, you should be the first

00:59:58.569 --> 01:00:02.824
to become the wisest.

01:00:06.018 --> 01:00:14.128
Maybe that the message of Sahaja Yoga should start more from Australia.

01:00:14.329 --> 01:00:19.025
So, go deep into yourself. Depth must be developed.

01:00:19.226 --> 01:00:22.521
They are still very fond of the sea and the sun,

01:00:22.722 --> 01:00:26.208
this they will do all their lives, there’s no need to worry about

01:00:26.409 --> 01:00:30.005
anything like that, it’s nothing important.

01:00:30.206 --> 01:00:33.278
The sea is within you, the sun is within you, the Atma is within you,

01:00:33.478 --> 01:00:37.828
everything is within you. Try to enjoy within.

01:00:38.029 --> 01:00:41.006
Give up the idea of going to the nature for it or anywhere,

01:00:41.207 --> 01:00:45.098
it’s within yourself, it’s all within.

01:00:45.298 --> 01:00:49.779
That is what I mean that if you look at things superficially,

01:00:49.980 --> 01:00:53.388
you take it from other people, now the craze of going out

01:00:53.589 --> 01:00:58.538
is finished in England, practically people don’t move out that way.

01:00:58.738 --> 01:01:04.029
Or they don’t go to the sea also to that extent.

01:01:04.230 --> 01:01:09.644
But, still in Australia, you have to learn all that.

01:01:09.845 --> 01:01:12.878
Instead of learning the hard way,

01:01:13.079 --> 01:01:20.107
it’s better to do it in a shorter way, is to become deeper and deeper.

01:01:20.501 --> 01:01:24.245
Cut down your activities, become deeper,

01:01:24.446 --> 01:01:29.888
meditate more than going to the sea.

01:01:30.089 --> 01:01:32.974
Sea visits are bit too much I think,

01:01:33.175 --> 01:01:39.137
also the sun bathing is also too much,

01:01:39.338 --> 01:01:41.637
is all very superficial.

01:01:41.838 --> 01:01:44.650
They all have liver problems, you shouldn’t go

01:01:44.851 --> 01:01:47.869
to the sun anymore, you should actually shut all your houses

01:01:48.070 --> 01:01:51.439
and sit down inside and meditate.

01:01:51.640 --> 01:01:54.773
What a problem we have of liver.

01:01:54.974 --> 01:01:57.898
So, do not treat any question superficially

01:01:58.099 --> 01:02:02.802
because God has given you, basically you are made of wisdom.

01:02:03.003 --> 01:02:05.998
You know, the whole soil has wisdom in it.

01:02:06.199 --> 01:02:09.606
But where is it, do you find it anywhere in Australia?

01:02:09.806 --> 01:02:11.861
It’s hard to find wise people, isn’t it?

01:02:12.062 --> 01:02:16.846
Sahaja Yogis can’t talk to other Australians, poor things.

01:02:17.047 --> 01:02:21.369
The reason is, you are following other people who are not all right.

01:02:21.570 --> 01:02:28.615
Follow yourself only. Go deep down, is wisdom there, lot of wisdom.

01:02:28.816 --> 01:02:32.591
Find out yourself, because you are wisdom,

01:02:32.792 --> 01:02:36.708
you will give wisdom to the whole world, it’s all like that you know,

01:02:36.909 --> 01:02:40.650
everywhere upside down conditions. In Australia,

01:02:40.851 --> 01:02:44.791
it should be wisdom personified; they are the most unwise people.

01:02:44.992 --> 01:02:48.057
They will always support the wrong type of people in their diplomacy.

01:02:48.258 --> 01:02:50.885
I mean all sorts of unwise things they do. Why?

01:02:51.086 --> 01:02:54.197
Because they have not gone to their own depths of finding out their wisdom.

01:02:54.397 --> 01:02:59.518
Like Maharashtrians have got Kundalini, they are sleeping.

01:02:59.718 --> 01:03:09.530
They are busy with this movement of going to this temple,

01:03:09.731 --> 01:03:16.794
for one month they will walk down to that temple and worship Shri Krishna there.

01:03:16.995 --> 01:03:20.575
They don’t want to see. And to add up to it,

01:03:20.776 --> 01:03:25.600
they take lot of tobacco in different ways. You see, even they use,

01:03:25.800 --> 01:03:30.958
what you call, o manjan, [Marathi]

01:03:31.159 --> 01:03:34.540
a kind of a powder made out of tobacco to rub their teeth,

01:03:34.741 --> 01:03:39.415
can you believe it? I mean teeth, which is Shri Krishna’s place.

01:03:39.616 --> 01:03:42.071
They rub it with this finger nicely

01:03:42.272 --> 01:03:48.054
and go to worship Shri Krishna there in the temple, absurd people.

01:03:48.254 --> 01:03:51.654
They take a little bit of this tobacco, mix it up with, to make it stronger,

01:03:51.855 --> 01:03:56.636
mix it up with a kind of a chuna, what you call,

01:03:56.837 --> 01:04:00.540
calcium carbonate, you see,  kind of a thing and put it here

01:04:00.741 --> 01:04:06.041
near these gums which is also Shri Krishna

01:04:06.242 --> 01:04:09.486
and go on singing for one month, not eat any food,

01:04:09.687 --> 01:04:12.900
do anything and go there and get their heads broken

01:04:13.101 --> 01:04:16.118
by these horrible Brahmins there.

01:04:16.319 --> 01:04:21.045
And this is Kundalini’s place, just imagine.

01:04:21.246 --> 01:04:26.627
Same in Europe which is the liver, which is the Nabhi.

01:04:26.827 --> 01:04:31.746
And they are the people who drink and eat.

01:04:31.955 --> 01:04:34.920
They consume more food than anybody else in the whole world

01:04:35.121 --> 01:04:38.175
can consume. You go to Spain, you are amazed,

01:04:38.376 --> 01:04:43.643
they can devour everyone.

01:04:46.076 --> 01:04:49.447
Then Americans, they also eat a lot.

01:04:49.647 --> 01:04:52.775
But Americans are, as I told you, they have no self-respect.

01:04:52.976 --> 01:04:55.932
No self- respect.

01:04:56.133 --> 01:04:58.828
They’ll give you five rupees and tell you hundred times,

01:04:59.029 --> 01:05:03.274
we have given you five rupees, five rupees, it is horrible.

01:05:03.475 --> 01:05:08.230
Those who do not have self-respect cannot respect another person.

01:05:08.431 --> 01:05:11.400
And they themselves can be parasitic, very parasitic,

01:05:11.601 --> 01:05:16.346
extremely parasitic people.

01:05:20.525 --> 01:05:24.236
There was an organization who wrote to Gavin,

01:05:24.437 --> 01:05:26.861
he was so angry with them. They said,

01:05:27.062 --> 01:05:31.515
"Mother is such a rich lady, why shouldn’t She pay

01:05:31.716 --> 01:05:36.749
for Her travel to America and also pay for their halls?

01:05:36.950 --> 01:05:43.130
We’ll give Her food." So he got very angry.

01:05:43.331 --> 01:05:48.823
I said, "No, tell them also I will pay for My food and yours also."

01:05:52.035 --> 01:05:56.576
And also get some nice presents for you. It’s all right.

01:05:56.777 --> 01:06:01.859
And they asked Me that, I went to a church and they said,

01:06:02.060 --> 01:06:05.171
"No, no we have to give You some money after all."

01:06:05.372 --> 01:06:07.819
I said, "Why?" They said, "It is a custom to have a collection."

01:06:08.020 --> 01:06:10.436
I said, "No, please don’t have." They had a collection,

01:06:10.637 --> 01:06:15.631
it was I think three dollar and two - what is cent of dollar, next to dollar?

01:06:15.832 --> 01:06:22.568
two cents, three dollar and two cents they collect.

01:06:22.769 --> 01:06:25.856
I mean, no self-respect of any kind, you know?

01:06:26.057 --> 01:06:30.598
They think whatever they do is all right, so ego-oriented, horrible.

01:06:30.799 --> 01:06:34.273
Always support wrong nations, always support wrong policies.

01:06:34.474 --> 01:06:37.091
Like they’ll support Argentina, Chileans

01:06:37.292 --> 01:06:41.124
who are horribly oppressive people.

01:06:41.325 --> 01:06:45.176
They have killed thousands and thousands of their civilians, simple people

01:06:45.377 --> 01:06:49.328
and just they are autocrats. All the Germans have reached there

01:06:49.528 --> 01:06:52.176
and the Germans are teaching them the fascism,

01:06:52.377 --> 01:06:55.852
the fascism is going to grow in these countries and take over these

01:06:56.053 --> 01:07:00.116
so-called peanut people.

01:07:00.317 --> 01:07:05.003
But they will support them and not Cuba, because it is communism.

01:07:05.204 --> 01:07:07.957
All right, communism is bad, democracy is good,

01:07:08.157 --> 01:07:12.309
what are you doing as democrats?

01:07:12.510 --> 01:07:15.488
You are supporting autocrats, always support wrong things.

01:07:15.689 --> 01:07:20.816
Made a mess in Vietnam, made a mess there, everywhere.

01:07:21.017 --> 01:07:23.603
They don’t know how to witness things properly.

01:07:23.804 --> 01:07:25.829
But they had Abraham Lincoln,

01:07:26.030 --> 01:07:29.595
so for that you have to excuse the whole country,

01:07:29.796 --> 01:07:35.411
but you can’t live with one Abraham Lincoln.

01:07:36.395 --> 01:07:39.294
These days Indians are horrible.

01:07:39.495 --> 01:07:42.379
I mean, you can kill somebody here

01:07:42.580 --> 01:07:47.235
and can pay some money and get out of it. This is what it is.

01:07:47.436 --> 01:07:51.815
The politicians put money when they want to have elections,

01:07:52.016 --> 01:07:54.091
so all wasters, all useless people

01:07:54.292 --> 01:07:59.563
are supported by business people here. The business people give money,

01:07:59.764 --> 01:08:05.061
the politicians fight elections and the whole is under the control

01:08:05.262 --> 01:08:08.280
of few business people who are miserly, horrible, absolutely useless,

01:08:08.481 --> 01:08:12.147
self-indulgent people.

01:08:12.348 --> 01:08:16.567
And these politicians take over, they are wasters,

01:08:16.768 --> 01:08:19.560
briefless lawyers, wasters, useless people

01:08:19.761 --> 01:08:23.665
who have no brains, they become ministers,

01:08:23.866 --> 01:08:29.121
it’s such a mess, everything for money.

01:08:30.662 --> 01:08:37.396
Anybody who is intelligent, cannot have much money, is a fact.

01:08:37.597 --> 01:08:40.208
It doesn’t go hand in hand.

01:08:40.409 --> 01:08:44.791
A person who is a worshipper of Saraswati doesn’t get so much Lakshmi.

01:08:44.992 --> 01:08:47.982
Always, you will find. You talk to a businessman,

01:08:48.183 --> 01:08:53.627
immediately you know, something is little loose.

01:08:55.182 --> 01:09:00.330
That’s true with Americans also, little loose.

01:09:01.846 --> 01:09:07.609
And if you talk to an intellectual, you find something very tight.

01:09:12.272 --> 01:09:15.406
This is the problem.

01:09:15.607 --> 01:09:18.710
And because of this, the money-oriented people in this country

01:09:18.911 --> 01:09:21.442
are stupid people.

01:09:21.643 --> 01:09:25.708
So you have to play into the hands of stupid people.

01:09:25.909 --> 01:09:30.225
Now, this is the country where the Yogeshwara lived.

01:09:30.426 --> 01:09:36.145
Great saints lived, they didn’t care for all the styles and all that.

01:09:36.346 --> 01:09:39.716
What is the need for Indians to have all these styles,

01:09:39.917 --> 01:09:43.802
they should live well, they should be clean, neat,

01:09:44.003 --> 01:09:48.614
they should not be insipid, because Lakshmi stays here.

01:09:48.815 --> 01:09:51.496
But the way they are becoming modern, you see, wearing nylons

01:09:51.697 --> 01:09:56.484
and having stainless steel in the house.

01:09:56.692 --> 01:09:59.129
For them, when I told them that I am going to make huts

01:09:59.375 --> 01:10:03.808
for your ashram, they were little bit [UNCLEAR].

01:10:08.473 --> 01:10:14.389
We are not going to have cements; I know Australians hate cement.

01:10:14.590 --> 01:10:18.092
We are not going to have cement, that’s one thing I am sure of.

01:10:18.293 --> 01:10:24.096
We can have stones, but no cements.

01:10:24.297 --> 01:10:30.481
You see, our ashram is going to be an ideal for everyone. It cannot be like any other.

01:10:30.682 --> 01:10:33.938
So don’t try to give Me examples of other ashrams.

01:10:34.139 --> 01:10:38.689
I am not going to take any hints from anyone.

01:10:39.760 --> 01:10:44.637
We are going to live in beautiful huts, very comfortably

01:10:44.838 --> 01:10:51.269
under the protection of Mother’s love.

01:10:52.909 --> 01:10:55.864
So, any other questions? From Australians, I had to drag in everybody,

01:10:56.073 --> 01:11:00.635
because I don’t want anybody to feel hurt.

01:11:08.787 --> 01:11:14.923
Never scold one person, scold at least ten then it’s all right.

01:11:22.523 --> 01:11:29.671
I am not going to say anything to him. Now what is it, what is the other question?

01:11:37.913 --> 01:11:40.538
Q: What to do with France, Mother?

01:11:40.739 --> 01:11:44.154
Shri Mataji: What is it?

01:11:45.102 --> 01:11:52.947
What is, what is France? I have already told you, France is a drunkard.

01:11:55.964 --> 01:11:58.793
And all the drunkards have no values left in them.

01:11:58.994 --> 01:12:03.989
They have no values about morality, no values at all.

01:12:04.190 --> 01:12:07.301
I mean, they are drunkards you see, no chetana,

01:12:07.502 --> 01:12:12.447
they are not aware, they are not human beings, they are drunk.

01:12:12.678 --> 01:12:17.882
That’s what they are. They are drunkards and they are supposed to be

01:12:18.083 --> 01:12:22.872
the Nabhi, the liver. Imagine, liver being drunk, horrible.

01:12:23.073 --> 01:12:27.841
But you don’t run away from France, all right?

01:12:29.083 --> 01:12:35.646
I know why he asked this question, they all want to run away.

01:12:42.797 --> 01:12:51.432
If you are a real French, you have to look after French people;

01:12:51.632 --> 01:12:53.789
it’s your duty, you are duty bound.

01:12:53.990 --> 01:12:56.633
If you are a Brahmin, you have to correct all the Brahmins,

01:12:56.834 --> 01:12:59.545
if you are Maratha, you have to correct all the Marathas.

01:12:59.746 --> 01:13:06.084
If you are really that, if I am an Indian, I have to correct Indians.

01:13:06.285 --> 01:13:09.560
I have to correct them; I have to bring them to the right path.

01:13:09.761 --> 01:13:16.652
Or should I also help them to go to hell?

01:13:17.535 --> 01:13:21.390
We have to look after them; they are your own people.

01:13:21.591 --> 01:13:26.862
To pull them out, even if you have one little bit

01:13:27.063 --> 01:13:30.766
of a sari in your hand, you can pull out the whole sari.

01:13:30.967 --> 01:13:36.184
Keep your grip there. That is wisdom.

01:13:36.385 --> 01:13:39.004
Nobody has to get out from anywhere; you settle down everywhere,

01:13:39.205 --> 01:13:41.848
I have settled you down for some purposes.

01:13:42.056 --> 01:13:49.583
Don’t have to shift; there is no need to shift. Nobody has to shift.

01:13:52.396 --> 01:13:55.951
Q: Mother, would You tell us Your secrets? You have been to the States,

01:13:56.152 --> 01:13:58.316
to Europe, to India, to Australia.

01:13:58.516 --> 01:14:04.696
What about South America, Africa, China and Japan?

01:14:05.494 --> 01:14:10.500
You see, I would suggest that all these countries

01:14:10.701 --> 01:14:14.888
are their part and parcel. But, as it is,

01:14:15.089 --> 01:14:18.584
we have many centers in our body, isn’t it? Not only seven.

01:14:18.785 --> 01:14:23.347
But we have to concentrate on first of all the seven major ones.

01:14:23.548 --> 01:14:25.722
So let us concentrate on these seven

01:14:25.923 --> 01:14:29.886
because we can operate also there, those we have already got, you see.

01:14:30.087 --> 01:14:34.808
Once you start working in those countries, I will talk about that also.

01:14:35.008 --> 01:14:39.157
Because at their back, I shouldn’t say anything.

01:14:39.358 --> 01:14:41.694
When they will be here, I will tell all about them.

01:14:41.895 --> 01:14:46.368
Africa is, God save them.

01:14:46.568 --> 01:14:49.294
I don’t know. As it is they were very good,

01:14:49.495 --> 01:14:52.153
but you people went and put your ideas into their heads.

01:14:52.354 --> 01:14:56.294
So, they are lost cases, absolutely lost cases.

01:14:56.495 --> 01:14:58.666
I don’t know. They have such organized religions

01:14:58.867 --> 01:15:02.034
and for primitive people, if you give them any organized religion,

01:15:02.235 --> 01:15:04.229
like Indian Christians are.

01:15:04.430 --> 01:15:08.882
They are one of the worst people we can think of, the Jews,

01:15:09.083 --> 01:15:16.182
Indian Jews, Indian Muslims, they are extremely fanatic,

01:15:16.383 --> 01:15:19.897
I mean extremely fanatic.

01:15:20.098 --> 01:15:22.600
Even you all Christians become Sahaja Yogis,

01:15:22.801 --> 01:15:25.834
the Indian Christians will not.

01:15:26.035 --> 01:15:29.848
For them, dog of the missionary is also to be worshipped.

01:15:30.049 --> 01:15:33.330
Yes, this is the case.

01:15:33.531 --> 01:15:38.452
That’s why I took My birth in that community.

01:15:38.653 --> 01:15:43.647
So this is what is. You have gone and converted them into Christianity.

01:15:43.848 --> 01:15:46.068
And there are, others are Muslims.

01:15:46.269 --> 01:15:49.777
They are very fanatic you see. A new Muslim eats

01:15:49.978 --> 01:15:54.284
lot of onions they say, because Indians don’t eat so much onions

01:15:54.485 --> 01:15:58.258
you see, so he eats more onions to prove that he is a good Muslim.

01:15:58.459 --> 01:16:01.813
That’s what it is. And you have harmed them very much

01:16:02.014 --> 01:16:07.818
by giving them Christianity, so called.

01:16:08.264 --> 01:16:12.334
I hope they will realize. The things will work out.

01:16:12.535 --> 01:16:14.904
We are working through Algeria; Algeria is taking shape,

01:16:15.105 --> 01:16:19.691
but it’s a autocratic country, all sorts of things are there.

01:16:19.892 --> 01:16:25.463
Let’s see, we have to depend on Sahaja Yoga and Sahaja Yogis.

01:16:25.664 --> 01:16:28.646
Sahaja Yogis more than anything. All right?

01:16:28.847 --> 01:16:32.854
May God bless you all.

01:16:34.449 --> 01:16:40.465
Question [Marathi]: What is Anaadi and Anahada?

01:16:49.348 --> 01:16:53.110
Shri Mataji: She has asked a nice question is that, "What is anadi and anahada?"

01:16:53.311 --> 01:17:04.176
Anahada is a sound that you hear; and she sees some colours.

01:17:05.358 --> 01:17:07.516
(Hindi): When you become the Atma,

01:17:07.717 --> 01:17:13.560
then nothing should be visible to you. You become that.

01:17:13.761 --> 01:17:19.067
When you come inside this, then nothing outside will be visible to you.

01:17:19.268 --> 01:17:23.642
The seeing of colors, when there is a movement to the right side of the Agnya,

01:17:23.843 --> 01:17:25.979
then you see start seeing the colors.

01:17:26.203 --> 01:17:33.786
The hearing of the sound or Anahada, that is talked about,

01:17:33.987 --> 01:17:39.833
this is also to be understood.

01:17:40.034 --> 01:17:44.545
The hearing of Anahad does not happen through these ears (external ears).

01:17:44.746 --> 01:17:48.123
When the ears inside us open, the sound of that

01:17:48.324 --> 01:17:53.518
is like the sound of sweet music.

01:17:53.718 --> 01:17:58.421
And that which is heard by external ears is not Anahad,

01:17:58.622 --> 01:18:02.021
it means that there is a problem of some kind.

01:18:02.222 --> 01:18:05.216
What this means is that either you have done lot of worship,

01:18:05.417 --> 01:18:08.294
for example, like chanting of the Gayatri mantra,

01:18:08.495 --> 01:18:13.902
then you will hear that sound, because by chanting of the Gayatri mantra,

01:18:14.103 --> 01:18:16.640
your movement is to the right side.

01:18:16.841 --> 01:18:20.137
Movement to the right side generates heat in you.

01:18:20.338 --> 01:18:24.189
Because of this heat, your nerves start getting dry.

01:18:24.390 --> 01:18:27.585
And when the nerves of the ear and nose become dry,

01:18:27.786 --> 01:18:31.252
because of this drying, these type of sounds start coming.

01:18:31.452 --> 01:18:34.881
That is entirely physical, and there is no joy in it.

01:18:35.082 --> 01:18:40.798
But when Anahad is heard internally, then in a way,

01:18:40.999 --> 01:18:44.011
it is not heard, but it is felt, for all things the rhythm manifests itself.

01:18:44.212 --> 01:18:46.512
It is not heard. Because of that a type of peace is felt within,

01:18:46.712 --> 01:18:48.670
a type of rhythm is felt within.

01:18:48.870 --> 01:18:51.441
Like when you hear some music, you start walking

01:18:51.641 --> 01:18:54.212
with a kind of a rhythm. In the same way,

01:18:54.412 --> 01:18:58.533
when the music inside starts, then it is not visible to you,

01:18:58.733 --> 01:19:04.219
but it actually happens in you.

01:19:04.511 --> 01:19:07.633
The rhythm starts manifesting in your talking

01:19:07.833 --> 01:19:13.498
and speaking, sweetness manifests. This is the difference.

01:19:13.699 --> 01:19:16.439
It doesn’t exist outside. You shouldn’t see the colours.

01:19:16.639 --> 01:19:18.851
Nothing should be seen. Understood?

01:19:19.052 --> 01:19:21.844
It has to be corrected, it will happen.

01:19:22.044 --> 01:19:24.727
[English] Her question, I answered...

01:19:24.928 --> 01:19:30.136
[Hindi] I will tell you, it is because of the Agnya chakra.

01:19:30.337 --> 01:19:34.560
It will happen by correcting the Agnya chakra.

01:19:34.761 --> 01:19:38.458
[English] She asked Me a question that you hear Anahad noises.

01:19:38.659 --> 01:19:41.769
She hears noises in her ear..

01:19:41.970 --> 01:19:48.040
If you see something is not subtle, finished.

01:19:59.068 --> 01:20:03.568
Any other question?

01:20:10.673 --> 01:20:18.210
If you stop one word "how", 90% questions will drop out.

01:22:46.964 --> 01:22:50.194
He asked me a question, "When we put a bandhan how long it will last?"

01:22:50.395 --> 01:22:55.489
I said, "Depends on your intensity." I never put any bandhan to myself.

01:22:55.689 --> 01:22:59.403
It is your intensity. After sometime, you don’t need any bandhan.

01:22:59.603 --> 01:23:05.359
Others will have to put bandhan when you go there.

01:23:21.648 --> 01:23:26.197
Yogi: (in Marathi): Where is the Hamsa Chakra?

01:23:31.603 --> 01:23:37.045
Hamsa. This is the Hamsa Cxhakra.

01:23:37.245 --> 01:23:41.037
It’s a very, very material thing, I think, this chakra, is very material.

01:23:41.237 --> 01:23:44.972
And it has to be worked on material level only.

01:23:45.172 --> 01:23:51.829
It’s the centre here where most of the Left and Right Sides,

01:23:52.029 --> 01:23:55.814
in a way, cross on a material level here, ‘material level’ again I say.

01:23:56.014 --> 01:24:00.390
On a material level they cross over here.

01:24:00.590 --> 01:24:03.944
And when it gets spoilt,

01:24:04.144 --> 01:24:08.967
you get troubles like sinus and troubles like colds

01:24:09.167 --> 01:24:12.787
and coughs and all that.

01:24:12.987 --> 01:24:17.847
So, I myself have tried to get this into trouble

01:24:18.047 --> 01:24:21.510
and to find out what I should do, because if I live as I am,

01:24:21.711 --> 01:24:24.389
I will never be able to help you. So, I said, "I better get sick Myself

01:24:24.590 --> 01:24:27.048
to see what happens."

01:24:27.248 --> 01:24:30.702
And actually, what happens with this centre catching,

01:24:30.902 --> 01:24:34.380
the same thing, the drying up of the nose, of the humidity,

01:24:34.580 --> 01:24:37.974
because of central heating is there.

01:24:38.174 --> 01:24:42.484
For Indians, and Maharashtrians especially take a kadak bath,

01:24:42.684 --> 01:24:44.778
means a very hot water.

01:24:44.979 --> 01:24:47.976
They use tremendously hot water to take their bath.

01:24:48.176 --> 01:24:51.396
For them it is very relaxing, which is an absolutely a wrong idea.

01:24:51.596 --> 01:24:55.486
Normally a cold bath is the best. If not possible,

01:24:55.687 --> 01:25:01.802
take a tepid, tepid water, can take

01:25:02.002 --> 01:25:04.950
little hot and then tepid, absolutely tepid water.

01:25:05.150 --> 01:25:09.933
That will solve one of the problems that you do not expose yourself to too much cold or heat,

01:25:10.134 --> 01:25:13.229
the temperature is kept the same as the room temperature.

01:25:13.430 --> 01:25:16.345
Because you take a very hot bath and then you come out.

01:25:16.545 --> 01:25:20.213
In London people have died, Indians have died out of their lung cancer,

01:25:20.414 --> 01:25:23.671
because they can’t get out of their habit,

01:25:23.871 --> 01:25:26.937
bad habit, of taking bath in the morning.

01:25:27.137 --> 01:25:32.990
I call it bad habit for Indians, not for English, eh?

01:25:34.307 --> 01:25:38.302
Because they’ll take their bath and immediately go to work.

01:25:38.502 --> 01:25:43.060
And so many Indians I have seen they have got lung cancer and they died there.

01:25:43.261 --> 01:25:46.511
And if you ask them, "Why?" "We don’t feel all right."

01:25:46.711 --> 01:25:50.571
Then take your bath at four o‘clock in the morning,

01:25:50.771 --> 01:25:54.508
stay in the house, get used to the climate and then go.

01:25:54.708 --> 01:25:59.371
Or take your bath in the night.

01:26:02.386 --> 01:26:04.638
All extreme behaviours, from left to right,

01:26:04.838 --> 01:26:09.247
create the problems of Hamsa.

01:26:09.447 --> 01:26:12.661
Like they’ll take, say, a fruit.

01:26:12.861 --> 01:26:14.832
I mean, we knew all these things but now we are modern, you see,

01:26:15.032 --> 01:26:20.098
we have forgotten. Like, you eat a banana in India, [Marathi]

01:26:20.298 --> 01:26:24.397
after that you should not take water.

01:26:24.606 --> 01:26:30.468
Old people know, but the young have become jeans-oriented.

01:26:30.668 --> 01:26:34.398
So, the whole head has gone into jeans.

01:26:34.598 --> 01:26:38.294
And they will eat banana and take water.

01:26:38.494 --> 01:26:41.364
Now these are two extremes. Any fruit you take

01:26:41.564 --> 01:26:47.378
and after that, you take water, you will get it.

01:26:47.578 --> 01:26:52.034
So, you should take water after some carbohydrates.

01:26:52.234 --> 01:26:56.258
You can take some papad, not fried one.

01:26:56.458 --> 01:27:01.185
Anything fried you take and on top of that you are not to take water.

01:27:01.386 --> 01:27:06.817
You can take a biscuit or you can have a, what you call, a bread,

01:27:07.018 --> 01:27:11.762
something like that to dry up. Best is chana.

01:27:11.962 --> 01:27:17.860
Dry up your throat and then take water.

01:27:20.289 --> 01:27:22.780
Heat and cold: now say take coffee and then take water,

01:27:22.980 --> 01:27:25.800
this is absolutely wrong. Water you should take

01:27:26.001 --> 01:27:28.372
then gradually heat it up and take coffee last,

01:27:28.572 --> 01:27:33.567
and then don’t take water till you have taken some carbohydrates.

01:27:33.767 --> 01:27:38.940
I mean, this is what it is, is the heat and the cold.

01:27:39.140 --> 01:27:44.735
The combination of heat and cold should be understood.

01:27:51.910 --> 01:27:56.267
Now what do you do?

01:27:57.947 --> 01:28:11.235
Actually, is to neglect certain laws of nature.

01:28:11.435 --> 01:28:15.899
Like in London or anywhere, it’s all heated up inside the rooms,

01:28:16.099 --> 01:28:18.811
too much heated up, and it’s very dry.

01:28:19.011 --> 01:28:23.662
And we all know that in England that you have to have a humidifier, isn’t it?

01:28:23.862 --> 01:28:28.112
You must keep some water or something

01:28:28.313 --> 01:28:31.360
or fill a tub in the bath, and keep it open

01:28:31.561 --> 01:28:36.805
so that there is humidity in the room.

01:28:37.006 --> 01:28:41.962
To compensate for all that, one can do is to take some water

01:28:42.162 --> 01:28:46.110
and sip in the nose.

01:28:46.310 --> 01:28:49.571
I would say, after brushing your teeth, sip it thrice

01:28:49.771 --> 01:28:53.389
and thrice you take it out. By putting these fingers,

01:28:53.589 --> 01:28:58.022
these thumbs in your ears and take it out.

01:28:58.222 --> 01:29:04.676
By that you’ll clear out your sinuses, you will make it humid.

01:29:04.876 --> 01:29:08.774
Or for these parched mucus membranes, you can put

01:29:08.975 --> 01:29:14.845
some oil or some ghee, is very good.

01:29:15.045 --> 01:29:20.187
If this water can have little salt, little salt, is a good idea.

01:29:20.387 --> 01:29:25.102
But that should not be very cold, should not be very hot, should be tepid.

01:29:25.303 --> 01:29:29.208
Tepid food.

01:29:29.408 --> 01:29:32.426
In India, the custom is to eat very hot food, garam.

01:29:32.626 --> 01:29:37.399
"Garam khao, garam garam khao." I mean, they are so garam.

01:29:39.102 --> 01:29:41.275
They are really garam people. I don’t know why.

01:29:41.475 --> 01:29:48.765
The man will sit on the thing and the woman must cook at that time garam-garam,

01:29:48.965 --> 01:29:52.312
and the rotis must be made at that time

01:29:52.512 --> 01:29:54.749
and the phulkas (chapatis) must be brought garam-garam.

01:29:54.949 --> 01:30:00.061
And the husband must eat garam-garam. And before going to office

01:30:00.262 --> 01:30:05.737
or work he should get garam-garam temperament also!

01:30:06.880 --> 01:30:08.939
Even they’ll say, "Leave this, leave this it’s not hot.

01:30:09.139 --> 01:30:12.963
We’ll bring hot for you!" And burning absolutely,

01:30:13.163 --> 01:30:16.868
you see, burning tongues, they are.

01:30:17.068 --> 01:30:20.993
There is no need to eat such a garam-garam business.

01:30:21.193 --> 01:30:24.194
On the contrary, in England they eat so much of cold foods

01:30:24.394 --> 01:30:28.131
that I am amazed! I mean ice, the amount of ice

01:30:28.331 --> 01:30:31.241
the Western people eat, we can’t understand.

01:30:31.441 --> 01:30:34.949
I mean how can you? Morning ice, every time ice,

01:30:35.149 --> 01:30:41.254
you have this thing with ice and "on the rocks," as they call it.

01:30:41.733 --> 01:30:44.955
So you will be on the rocks! (Laughter)

01:30:45.155 --> 01:30:48.500
So much of ice they take. God knows why.

01:30:48.700 --> 01:30:51.109
What is the need to take so much of ice?

01:30:51.309 --> 01:30:57.185
Indiscriminately they’ll take ice-cream. After ice-cream they’ll take coffee.

01:30:57.385 --> 01:31:01.865
Or after coffee they’ll take ice-cream.

01:31:02.065 --> 01:31:05.244
I mean, it’s such a national dish there, ice.

01:31:05.445 --> 01:31:08.988
Icing, icing, icing. All the time so much of ice.

