[Marathi]

02:23:09.943 --> 02:23:18.291
So when you are doing any action,

02:23:18.492 --> 02:23:24.864
because you are not doing it, you take the ego upon yourself.

02:23:25.544 --> 02:23:28.701
You think you are doing it.

02:23:28.902 --> 02:23:33.352
So the ego develops.

02:23:34.333 --> 02:23:38.413
All your karmas are just like driving, you see?

02:23:38.614 --> 02:23:41.911
Without having a car there just driving. "You see, I'm driving,

02:23:42.112 --> 02:23:44.775
I'm driving a car." "Where is the car?"

02:23:44.975 --> 02:23:50.447
"No I'm driving", working very hard.

02:23:52.003 --> 02:23:54.030
So that is the karma.

02:23:54.231 --> 02:23:58.586
So Karma Yoga means when you get the driver.

02:23:58.787 --> 02:24:05.107
When the car gets the driver, then there is a yoga.

02:24:06.893 --> 02:24:10.358
Now, Layla Yoga is that where

02:24:10.566 --> 02:24:15.256
you don't have to worry about these two things

02:24:15.456 --> 02:24:19.524
that "I'm doing this work",

02:24:19.724 --> 02:24:22.591
nor you have to worry that "I have cleared."

02:24:22.792 --> 02:24:26.466
When it happens? When you become an expert.

02:24:26.667 --> 02:24:30.944
You don't think you're driving. You don't have to remember.

02:24:31.144 --> 02:24:35.346
And you don't have to learn anymore, when you are learning is over.

02:24:35.547 --> 02:24:38.856
When does it happen?

02:24:39.057 --> 02:24:41.991
Is when you put the driver inside yourself,

02:24:42.192 --> 02:24:45.600
when you become the driver. So when does it happen?

02:24:45.801 --> 02:24:48.499
When you get realized. How do you get realized?

02:24:48.699 --> 02:24:52.701
By Kundalini awakening? Through what? Through Sajaha Yoga.

02:24:52.902 --> 02:24:58.230
And who does that? Mataji Nirmala Devi.

02:25:27.394 --> 02:25:29.344
That's true.

02:25:29.544 --> 02:25:32.160
Yes, what I'm saying that there is no connection,

02:25:32.360 --> 02:25:34.453
so what bhakti you are doing?

02:25:34.654 --> 02:25:39.309
See if there's no connection with this, no use using this.

02:25:39.510 --> 02:25:43.080
You see, it has no meaning. This instrument of bhakti is useless.

02:25:43.281 --> 02:25:46.956
It is not working. But when I say that,

02:25:47.156 --> 02:25:52.796
all hot-tempered people will come out with their big, big stomach.

02:25:52.997 --> 02:25:58.598
And try to hit Me hard, I don't care.

02:27:00.250 --> 02:27:05.180
[Marathi]

02:27:39.278 --> 02:27:43.842
And he is just

02:27:44.043 --> 02:27:48.773
saying something sweeter now,

02:27:48.974 --> 02:27:52.661
that...

02:27:59.794 --> 02:28:01.989
It is embarrassing.

02:28:02.190 --> 02:28:06.049
[Marathi]

02:28:09.642 --> 02:28:14.494
I told them that you have got the [Marathi].

02:28:15.530 --> 02:28:17.621
Setting, you have got the setting all right.

02:28:17.822 --> 02:28:22.048
And I have found the diamonds, you better set it there.

02:28:23.118 --> 02:28:27.766
What is the setting just here?

02:28:31.384 --> 02:28:34.360
Why should you feel embarrassed? I mean, I should feel embarrassed.

02:28:34.560 --> 02:28:38.509
Why should you?

02:31:48.332 --> 02:31:53.543
Listen to the radio every day, they have couplet like this

02:31:53.744 --> 02:31:58.274
which say that the one who sees the Parabrahma

02:31:58.475 --> 02:32:04.961
in the in a form in Saguna, with the Gunas

02:32:05.162 --> 02:32:08.919
is the luckiest person in the world, most fortunate.

02:32:09.120 --> 02:32:13.414
But how many of us are really fortunate?

02:32:13.615 --> 02:32:17.499
Is that mother should say, see for herself

02:32:17.700 --> 02:32:24.205
that She is Parabrahma and She is in form, you are the luckiest people.

02:32:24.406 --> 02:32:29.048
That's true also, no doubt.

02:32:29.250 --> 02:32:33.398
I'm also very lucky.

02:32:33.835 --> 02:32:35.701
[Marathi]

02:32:35.902 --> 02:32:41.206
Where do you get mirrors?

02:33:01.539 --> 02:33:08.781
That we don't do anything. Everything is done by Mother.

02:33:08.982 --> 02:33:12.699
Is a good idea.

02:33:25.111 --> 02:33:29.307
[Marathi]

02:33:57.487 --> 02:34:02.878
[Marathi]

02:34:04.400 --> 02:34:07.994
When I'm speaking also, you should not keep your eyes closed.

02:34:08.195 --> 02:34:15.007
Better, but when you are meditating, you can close your eyes.
